questions.question: What is ComfyUI SimpleTools Suit?
questions.answer: This is a small set of simple nodes that help your workflow on ComfyUI.
questions.subject: ComfyUI SimpleTools Suit

questions.question: What does the Simple Google Translator node allow the user to do?
questions.answer: This node allows the user to write down their prompt in any language.
questions.subject: Simple Google Translator

questions.question: What is the purpose of the Simple Resolution Solver node?
questions.answer: The purpose of the Simple Resolution Solver is to help users calculate width and height that works with their model.
questions.subject: Simple Resolution Solver
